&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Salary range: $17-26/hr. Factors including past experience and location may affect final compensation rate.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
