&lt;p&gt;EquipmentShare’s Architectural Designer role involves upholding design standards, managing projects from inception to post-occupancy evaluation, collaborating with various stakeholders, and staying current with industry trends.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Primary Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
