&lt;li&gt;Establish project goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee small teams to produce designs on multiple projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist team members with project budgets and timelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute multiple designs under various deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate stated design principles/objectives into unique and varied store locations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, analyze and solve design and construction problems in a collaborative manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop form, proportion, scale and materiality of a variety of architectural projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure building systems are aesthetically pleasing, functional, reliable and safe - a working knowledge of building codes and familiarity with health requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in onsite visits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work independently with minimal supervision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Read, interpret and explain complex technical documents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
