&lt;li&gt;Prepare sketches or renderings to demonstrate preliminary designs to various internal stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize design software to prepare and illustrate final plans, renderings and construction documents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure project success by performing post-occupancy evaluations&lt;/li&gt;
